{"tid":196899,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"無待堂評鄭松泰被捕","createTime":"2017-04-11T14:53:15.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-11T16:49:02.000Z","uid":30807,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a8ed673a6f4326704ddcde4534950915a23bfb57","tid":196899,"uid":30807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T14:53:15.000Z","msg":"警察拘捕鄭松泰，是繼DQ梁遊之後，似乎是進一步將立法會「人大化」的工程之一，除了減低立法會實然的政治能量之外，立法會的直選議席，是香港政制中極少數能直接代表民意的機制。「一國兩制白皮書」講明「執行上」的一國兩制，是「中央擁有對香港特別行政區的全面管治權」，而這個權力主要是透過行政長官去行使，行政的權力必然是以立法作為制衡權力的消退，作為實現手段。<br />\n<br />\n在人大化的立法會，不能控制或者難以控制的人都會被行政權力用各種方法打擊。比較「溫和」，立法會秘書處擴權，連主席都變成花瓶如是，乃至用警察拘捕議員，幫你處理立法會事務也一樣。無關法律，行政方當然明白這樣做會有政治效果，但也許這種令其他議員和黨派恐懼的政治效果，也許正是他們想要的。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=10212528728430120&amp;id=1140397154\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D10212528728430120%26id%3D1140397154&d=pQk%2FYDfxyk1It%2BdH9Wj1W5Uc5Mn1qk%2F8nAzLhrzJJK4%3D&h=33e1c646\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=10212528728430120&amp;id=1140397154</a>"},{"pid":"8aa67bff758642e49c61f59b2b21d7a5a86fcccb","tid":196899,"uid":90863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T14:56:56.000Z","msg":"收皮啦腎弟"},{"pid":"d01c115b8ca1a0e8ede9270f47039a20f83e479e","tid":196899,"uid":30807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T14:58:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>收皮啦腎弟</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"684691f464a89de64d89df8027319ab7d3b6b227","tid":196899,"uid":48157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T16:42:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8ec89f46ee7d13d1e10d8d72b60c60fbe58c5ac4","tid":196899,"uid":50719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T16:47:37.000Z","msg":"WFC"},{"pid":"9414bdc04152a2bf7726ba7ac4fb53a694653ffd","